<L>__{interior walter's apt. night}
<A>__{walter sits at his table, a scrap of wood in his hand. he whittles away at the wood. it is the rough outline of a heart with wings. there is a loud knock on the door. walter gets up. the knock comes again, even harder. walter goes to the door and opens it. the smiles fades from his face. sergeant lucas pushes the door open further and walks right in. he wears a well tailored suit.}
<C>__{lucas}
<D>__{hiya, walter.}
<C>__{walter}
<D>__{cop.}
<C>__{man}
<D>__{sergeant lucas.}
<P>__{(flashes his badge)}
<D>__{may i come in?}
<C>__{walter}
<D>__{you are in.}
<C>__{lucas}
<D>__{so i am. but i always like to ask.}
