<C>__{lucas}
<D>__{cherry?}
<C>__{walter}
<D>__{yeah.}
<C>__{lucas}
<D>__{unusual design for a contemporary piece.}
<A>__{lucas runs his hand along the surface.}
<C>__{walter}
<D>__{it's not for sale.}
<C>__{lucas}
<D>__{who said i wanted to buy it?}
